data = {u'development': [{u'picture': u'', u'name': u'Instagram Challenge', u'service': u'photo app', u'skills': u'#python #PIL', u'company_url': u'http://instagram-engineering.tumblr.com/post/12651721845/instagram-engineering-challenge-the-unshredder', u'my_work_url': u'https://github.com/ashaegupta/unshredder', u'description': u'Totally got addicted to this instagram engineering challenge. Task: Fix a shredded and scrambled image. '}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'SplitMyRide', u'service': u'taxi-sharing service', u'skills': u'#python #mongodb #AmazonEC2 #tornado\xc2\xa0', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'https://github.com/ashaegupta/Split-My-Ride', u'description': u'Wrote all server-side code for a taxi-sharing service that matches people taking cabs from New York airports to Manhattan / Brooklyn.'}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'Venmo', u'service': u'android app', u'skills': u'#start-up #android #java #mobile #api', u'company_url': u'http://venmo.com', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'Picked up android programming as it was a high need at the time for the start-up.'}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'pod', u'service': u'web app', u'skills': u'#python #tornado #html #beautifulsoup', u'company_url': u'http://www.srb.ag/pod', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': "Pulls and displays photos from a flickr account that were taken on today's date in any previous year."}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'DrinksOnMe', u'service': u'android app', u'skills': u'#android #java #mobile #api', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'A foursquare-venmo mash-up that allows you to buy a drink (on Venmo) for anyone checked-in to the same location as you (on foursquare). Basically a pick-up tool for the shy geek in some of us.'}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'Search Algorithm', u'service': u'class project', u'skills': u'#java #search-algorithm', u'company_url': u'https://github.com/ashaegupta/InvIndexSearch', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'A comparison of the efficiency of two different search methods for searching through a body of documents: term-at-a-time and document-at-a-time. Term-at-a-time is optimal for shorter, rare query terms, while doc-at-a-time is preferred for longer and more frequent queries.'}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'Gmail Analysis', u'service': u'class project', u'skills': u'#R #python #IMAP #gmail', u'company_url': u'http://chippertohacker.tumblr.com/post/11403460242/r-project-email-analysis', u'my_work_url': u'https://github.com/ashaegupta/R_Project_Gmail_Analysis', u'description': "We spend so much of our time and interaction on email now! I wrote an R package that downloads a user's email history, conducts text analysis and graphs results. What time of day are you most likely to reply to an email? What day of week? How many emails do you send per day?"}], u'product': [{u'picture': u'http://dl.dropbox.com/u/9927844/Jing/2012-02-10_2354.png', u'name': u'Venmo', u'service': u'mobile payment service', u'skills': u'#start-up #user-research #user-experience #mock-ups #cross-team-collaboration #manager\xe2\x80\xa8', u'company_url': u'http://venmo.com', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'People didn\'t immediately trust Venmo as a financial service and there was a high drop off during sign-up flow. We designed product features and communication to increase security, evoke trust and build a sense of Venmo "community". Making friends\' activity more prominent was a key "community" builder. New app to be launched soon.'}, {u'picture': u'http://dl.dropbox.com/u/9927844/Jing/2012-02-10_2357.png', u'name': u'Yiftee', u'service': u'micro-gifting service', u'skills': u'#start-up #user-research \xc2\xa0#strategy #prototyping', u'company_url': u'http://yiftee.com', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': "Small business owners are incredibly busy with difficult-to-integrate POSs. They don't have time to analyze rich customer data or train employees on new offerings. Their bottom-line is their primary concern. Therefore, the team pivoted from initial customer data product to a digital gift-giving service that was much lower touch and had a more direct impact on revenue."}, {u'picture': u'http://dl.dropbox.com/u/9927844/Jing/2012-02-10_2356.png', u'name': u'MoveTogether', u'service': u'taxi-sharing service', u'skills': u'#start-up #user-research #mock-ups #user-experience #cross-team-implementation #management', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'http://dthink.srb.ag/post/16748438250/movetogether-lessons-learned-from-ethnography-and-the', u'description': u'Ridesharing is a difficult two-sided, supply-driven market problem. It\xe2\x80\x99s hard to incentivize drivers to offer a ride as they prize convenience and their quiet, personal time. However, ridesharing was more successful amongst close-knit communities. Therefore, my team pivoted to a one-sided market: taxi-sharing amongst the business community. We prototyped at the GoogleI/0 conference in 2011, matching rides to and from SFO. It was a big success.'}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'Sigma-Dek', u'service': u'DIY Outdoor Deck', u'skills': u'#start-up #user-research #prototyping', u'company_url': u'http://sigmadek.com/', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': "People desire the emotional satisfaction of building a deck themselves instead of contracting it out. But they want to be able to build the deck in a weekend and without many obscure tools. Therefore, the team prototyped (and eventually built) a simple snap-in-place deck kit. Pieces snap together, but are still stable, safe and strong, and the entire deck can be built in 45 minutes. It's now sold across North America."}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'Marketing White Paper', u'service': u'monitor project', u'skills': u'#corporate #marketing', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'A re-look on the traditional advertising mantra: market, media, message. Effective global brands, also consider "moment" - when are users most inclined to be receptive, and how can you create in-store experiences that make emotional connections with your customers. Wrote a white paper on good examples of the 4Ms.'}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'Canadian Teleco', u'service': u'monitor project', u'skills': u'#corporate #user-research #user-experience #cross-team-implementation', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'Assessed potential needs and economic viability of new market segments for a local Canadian Teleco that was looking to expand nationally.'}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'Canadian National Newspaper', u'service': u'monitor project', u'skills': u'', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u''}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'Legal Services Company', u'service': u'monitor project', u'skills': u'#corporate #user-research #product-offering #M&A\xc2\xa0', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'Assessed industry trends and user needs to recommend expansion into more semantic-based search discovery products. This was an important shift away from typical text-based search methods'}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'National Grocery Chain', u'service': u'monitor project', u'skills': u'#user-research', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u''}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'Global Pharmaceutical', u'service': u'monitor project', u'skills': u'#implementation #market-entry #marketing #product-education', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'Helped implement a pilot program for an alternative revenue model based on preventative care and education.\xc2\xa0Collaborated closely with client to develop training materials and conduct workshops to train new product ambassadors.'}], u'data_mantra': u'Intuition is fantastic, intuition backed by robust data, even better.', u'personal': [{u'picture': u'', u'name': u'YogaProject', u'service': u'', u'skills': u'#teaching', u'company_url': u'http://www.srb.ag/yoga', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'I made this series of yoga videos for friends in Asia, where unfortunately good yoga classes are not readily available.'}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'Splash', u'service': u'', u'skills': u'#education #teaching #math', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'Taught kids in East Palo Alto, an hour long seminar on "Things I wish I learned when I was your age". Topics included how to make decisions, how to deal with feedback in work and relationships, and an introduction to cognitive heuristics we all have to watch out for.'}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'Mzcombozi Secondary', u'service': u'high school in Tanzania', u'skills': u'#education #teaching #math', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'Taught 8th grade math to 40 students who sat in 20 desks. The thrill of seeing their faces when a concept clicked is still one of the greatest moments in my life. I had to do a lot of laundry during those 5 weeks because I typically came home covered in chalk dust.'}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'CatchPhrase', u'service': u'arduino game', u'skills': u'#arduino', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'First arduino hack. User presses a button to prompt a new random phrase from a previously programmed list. Word is displayed on an LCD screen. Good for charades and studying.'}], u'product_mantra': "I believe the secret to great products is to continually ask 'why?' and then serve that deepest need.", u'development_mantra': u'Everyone should be able to write and understand code at a basic level.', u'data': [{u'picture': u'', u'name': u'National Cable Provider', u'service': u'monitor project', u'skills': u'#excel #management #cross-collaboration #CLV', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'In the past, decisions at this company had largely been driven by instinct and intuition of leadership. With the changing landscape in media, the company needed to better understand their customers and product lines quantitatively. Therefore, my team developed a customer-life-time value model to identify high-profit and low-profit customers, which customers are worth trying to keep, and what product lines are associated with lowest churn.'}, {u'picture': u'', u'name': u'Global Pharmaceutical', u'service': u'monitor project', u'skills': u'#corporate #excel #war-game-simulation', u'company_url': u'', u'my_work_url': u'', u'description': u'Modeled '}], u'personal_mantra': u'Life is what happens when you busy are making other plans. Spend time on things you care about.'}
